.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心最近發現自己彈fingerstyle遇上瓶頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好無奈好似陣極都進步唔到<br />\n有冇前輩或者有彈開fingerstyle既人一齊分享下技巧?<br />\n我而家勉強都彈到一半sungha jung既歌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n彈到一半都好勁啦 教我ok?</blockquote><br />\n點教?我覺得自己彈得好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1f6bb1355cc6eb33761741fc68d7cdae144eb3","tid":9713,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:06:56.000Z","msg":"好難揾到譜彈<br />\n同咪彈都係靠死記<br />\n完全唔明點解係咁樣禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7440cd2842476869befe45ba404a480d27dc84be","tid":9713,"uid":36165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:20:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好難揾到譜彈<br />\n同咪彈都係靠死記<br />\n完全唔明點解係咁樣禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都幾易搵到譜，我指係sungha jung個d啦，如果流行曲就通常都冇，除非咁禁岩有人編左份譜<br />\n彈fingerstyle唔洗死記,我通常都係睇住個譜彈<br />\n可能你唔太熟結他啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af3cfa7f57a2e7bcb1686d8e4c7928e92d30d43","tid":9713,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好難揾到譜彈<br />\n同咪彈都係靠死記<br />\n完全唔明點解係咁樣禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都幾易搵到譜，我指係sungha jung個d啦，如果流行曲就通常都冇，除非咁禁岩有人編左份譜<br />\n彈fingerstyle唔洗死記,我通常都係睇住個譜彈<br />\n可能你唔太熟結他啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自學 同玩既時間短<br />\n所以真係唔太識<br />\n主要靠死記 個chord點解咁禁其實無理過<br />\n<br />\n普通人睇我彈會以為我好勁 <br />\n可以彈到fingerstyle ( 流行曲 )<br />\n其實只係咁岩揾到譜 跟住啲數字彈死背譜<br />\n<br />\n其實想知啲人點編譜<br />\n好多歌想彈 ( 流行曲 ) 但無人編放上網分享<br />\n就無得彈... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bd7457d59bb5b844502ecdc4d89a6d384aeb4e","tid":9713,"uid":32835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"